#Rest Log Viewer

This is a log viewer for #rest on irc.freenode.net
Feel free to fork and make changes.  
Pull requests will be handled promptly.

Sample Apache VHost:
<VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName rest.local
    DocumentRoot /home/kev/web/rest/dev
    <Directory   /home/kev/web/rest/dev>
        AllowOverride All
    </Directory>
    SetEnv APP_ENV local     # <-- IMPORTANT
</VirtualHost>

